//|                         A contains interleaved real/imaginary    |
//|                         values                                   |
//| * real FFT plan     -   sizeof(A)=2*N,                           |
//|                         A contains real values interleaved with  |
//|                         zeros                                    |
//| * real FHT plan     -   sizeof(A)=2*N,                           |
//|                         A contains real values interleaved with  |
//|                         zeros                                    |
//+------------------------------------------------------------------+
